author: Jay Solomon
title: Kerry Meets With Netanyahu, Pushes Israelis and Palestinians for End to Violence
text:
BERLIN—Secretary of State John Kerry met Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu on Thursday and pressed Israelis and Palestinians to take clear steps to de-escalate violence and attempt to return to a peace process.
It is absolutely critical to end all incitement and all violence and find a road forward to build a possibility, that is not there today, for a larger process,” Mr. Kerry said in remarks made ahead of his meeting with...
